# 🧠 Document Butler · RAG API
## ✨ Features

- 📄 **Multi‑format** – PDF, DOCX, MD, CSV, TXT  
- ⚡ **Streaming answers** – token‑by‑token via SSE  
- 🔗 **Source references** – every answer links to the original chunk  
- 🗑️ **Document management** – list / delete uploaded files  
- 🎨 **Dark UI** – built with React + Vite  

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Backend
```bash
git clone <repo>
cd fastapi_rag_project
python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
# edit .env with your Qdrant & OpenAI keys
python main.py

Frontend (separate terminal)
bash
npm create vite@latest document-butler -- --template react
cd document-butler
npm install
# copy src/DocumentButler.jsx from this repo
npm run dev
